For example, we're
a software company.

00:22:38.050 --> 00:22:40.782
Then looking at the
pharmaceutical company,

00:22:40.782 --> 00:22:43.400
they may have a similar
process that I can borrow from.

00:22:43.400 --> 00:22:44.000
LEIGH THOMPSON:
Oh, that's great.

00:22:44.000 --> 00:22:45.333
I love-- what's your first name?

00:22:45.333 --> 00:22:46.100
AUDIENCE: Sam.

00:22:46.100 --> 00:22:46.950
LEIGH THOMPSON: Sam.

00:22:46.950 --> 00:22:47.450
All right.

00:22:47.450 --> 00:22:51.350
So Sam is saying, I am in the
computer software industry.

00:22:51.350 --> 00:22:52.880
But maybe they're
