00:22:57.990 --> 00:23:00.200
borrow, and steal that idea.

00:23:00.200 --> 00:23:02.240
So now I want you to
predict something.

00:23:02.240 --> 00:23:07.940
This is some research I did
with my colleague [INAUDIBLE].

00:23:07.940 --> 00:23:09.560
I love to study teams.

00:23:09.560 --> 00:23:13.550
Heather knows how interested
I am in your teens at Google.

00:23:13.550 --> 00:23:16.360
We did a very controlled
study in which--

00:23:16.360 --> 00:23:19.220
and it's all about
innovation and creativity--

00:23:19.220 --> 00:23:21.230
some groups stayed
intact, meaning

00:23:21.230 --> 00:23:24.080
that you work with
the same people,

00:23:24.080 --> 00:23:26.640
and you didn't
change up membership.

00:23:26.640 --> 00:23:30.950
You're working on the same
problem, innovation problem.

00:23:30.950 --> 00:23:36.567
Other groups stayed intact
except at periodic times.

00:23:36.567 --> 00:23:37.400
What your fist name?

00:23:37.400 --> 00:23:38.100
AUDIENCE: Boris.

00:23:38.100 --> 00:23:39.016
LEIGH THOMPSON: Boris.

00:23:39.016 --> 00:23:42.720
Except at certain periods,
Boris would come into the group,

00:23:42.720 --> 00:23:43.970
and somebody else would leave.

00:23:43.970 --> 00:23:45.690
So it was what we
called open groups.

00:23:45.690 --> 00:23:50.690
So in other words, we're
about 75% to 85% intact,

00:23:50.690 --> 00:23:52.400
but we're having
some people go and--

00:23:52.400 --> 00:23:53.900
it's not a total changeup.

00:23:53.900 --> 00:23:56.450
It's just what we
called an interloper.

00:23:56.450 --> 00:23:59.060
And then they had to do
a brainstorming task.

00:23:59.060 --> 00:24:06.040
What's your hypothesis, Boris?

00:24:06.040 --> 00:24:08.960
Who's more innovative, the
open or the closed groups?

00:24:11.648 --> 00:24:13.000
AUDIENCE: The open groups.

00:24:13.000 --> 00:24:14.166
LEIGH THOMPSON: Open groups.

00:24:14.166 --> 00:24:16.570
And why would that--
let's imagine everybody--

00:24:16.570 --> 00:24:18.910
it's not like you're inviting
in Einstein or anything,

00:24:18.910 --> 00:24:20.470
but say more.

